**Example 1: 创建IPV6转换实例**

创建IPV6转换实例

Input: 

```
tccli vpc CreateIp6Translators --cli-unfold-argument  \
    --Ip6TranslatorCount 1
```

Output: 
```
{
    "Response": {
        "Ip6TranslatorSet": [
            "ip6-90pt7p9q"
        ],
        "RequestId": "aa645287-23fa-4950-8dc4-c56e63d2ca87"
    }
}
```
